snippet.title: Condor 3 -  The Weather
snippet.description:
Unexpectedly, we have to delay the release by a few days. Our excellent beta team have uncovered some issues we need to resolve and retest. Please be assured we are putting every effort into releasing as soon as possible.

We give you this video to watch in the meantime. Note there is sound in the video.


Video made by Wiek Schoenmakers.
